data.description: Follow the road and at the end you will see this Beautiful 3 bedroom and 2-bathroom TRUE LOG, FULLY FURNISHED Home nestled privately inside almost 2 acres. Enjoy the mountain views and the sounds of nature from either your large covered patio or covered deck. The wood interior really makes this home a cozy cabin that features a large kitchen with plenty of cabinets opened to the living area with a beautiful stone gas fireplace. A Large bedroom, bathroom and laundry area conveniently located on the main floor. The second-level features vaulted ceilings with 2 bedrooms that have access to the large deck and second bathroom. Don't forget the large shed/MAN CAVE!! Located inside the Equestrian Community of Shepard Farm, you can enjoy being in the country with only a short drive to town!
